title: Easy Living and Endless Amenities!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
